<div class="panel">
    <div class="panel-heading">
        <div class="panel-actions">
            <a href="#" class="fa fa-caret-down"></a>
        </div>

        <p class="panel-title">InetSCHOOLS <i class="fa fa-angle-right fa-fw"></i> Parents & élèves
    </div>
    <div class="panel-body">
        <p>Cher parents/élèves, un cours a été programmé dans l'enseigne : {{ enseigne_nom }}. <br>Les détails du cours sont les suivants: </p>
        <table class="table table-bordered" style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: center;">
            <thead style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: center;">
                <tr style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: center;">
                    <th style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: center;">Classe</th>
                    <th style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: center;">Libelle cours</th>
                    <th style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: center;">Date</th>
                    <th style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: center;">Heure</th>
                    <th style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: center;">Description</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: center;">
                <tr style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: center;">
                    <td scope="row" style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: center;">{{ classe }}</td>
                    <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: center;">{{ cours }}</td>
                    <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: center;">{{ date_cours }} </td>
                    <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: center;">{{ debut_heure }} à {{ fin_heure }}</td>
                    <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: center;">description</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        <p> <a href="{{ path('timeline', {'id_enseigne' : id_enseigne}) }}">Consulter timeline</a> </p>
    </div>
    <div class="panel-footer">
        <p class="m-none"><small>{{ "now"|date("m/d/Y H:i:m") }}</small></p>
    </div>
</div>